---
title: Greek Chicken Pizza with Two Cheese and Peppers
description: We’re unlocking the secret to delicious, easy pizza dinners by using Greek pitas as a base. This week, we top the flatbread with all of the healthy and delicious Greek flavours you love;  juicy peppers, tangy feta, and tender chicken. It’s quick, easy, and will have you saying OPA in no time!
